27
00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:21.419
regular stickers instead.

28
00:03:21.980 --> 00:03:24.899
Curious, you attach the
stickers to the child's legs.

29
00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:27.279
The child's task
is to remove them.

30
00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:29.499
Pay attention to
the arms and legs.

31
00:03:29.900 --> 00:03:32.249
We remove the sticker
from the left leg with the

32
00:03:32.260 --> 00:03:34.179
