37
00:06:56.100 --> 00:06:58.989
This is an exercise you will
do together with your child.

38
00:07:00.070 --> 00:07:03.259
You both lie on your stomachs
facing each other at a

39
00:07:03.270 --> 00:07:06.699
distance of one point five
to two meters, and roll

40
00:07:06.710 --> 00:07:09.619
the ball to each other,
stretching your arms out.

41
00:07:10.430 --> 00:07:13.259
When you catch the ball, you
need to hold it over your head

42
00:07:13.270 --> 00:07:16.799
for two seconds, then lower
your head to the floor,

43
00:07:16.810 --> 00:07:19.839
relaxing the neck and
back muscles, then rise

44
00:07:19.850 --> 00:07:21.209
again and roll the ball.

45
00:07:21.870 --> 00:07:25.099
Repeat for five minutes
or longer if the child

46
00:07:25.110 --> 00:07:26.229
wants to keep playing.

47
00:07:27.010 --> 00:07:30.239
Don't forget to enjoy the time
you spend with your child,

48
00:07:30.250 --> 00:07:32.509
even if at the same time
you are actually helping

49
00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:34.329
them integrate reflexes.

